{
    include "registries/aaosa_basic.hocon" 

    # Optional metadata describing this agent network
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simple agent network using a single LLM-based agent",
        "tags": ["example"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "Provide ground clearance flight AF84. The aircraft is a B747 that has landed one minute ago on runway 28L. It will park at gate A1.", 
            "Flight AF84 has landed on runway 28L. The aircraft is a B747 and it has been assigned to gate A1. "
        ]
    },

    "llm_config": {
        "model_name": "gpt-4o",
    },
    "max_iterations": 40000, #3000 
    "max_execution_seconds": 7200, #600
    "commondefs": {
        "replacement_strings": {
            "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of aircraft turnaround process at an Airport. 
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,
            "aaosa_instructions": """
When you receive an inquiry, you will:
1. If you are clearly not the right agent for this type of inquiry, reply you're not relevant.
2. If there is a chance you're relevant, call your down-chain agents to determine if they can answer all or part of the inquiry.
   Do not assume what your down-chain agents can do. Always call them. You'll be surprised.
3. Once all relevant down-chain agents have responded, either:
   - Analyze their response and compile your final response. No need to include non-relevant agents. In doubt, ask for clarification.
   - Follow up with your down-chain agents if needed, as many times as needed
   - If an action is needed, ask the most relevant down-chain agent to fulfill the inquiry.
4. Return the final response to the caller.
You may, in turn, be called by other agents in the system and have to act as a down-chain agent to them. 
            """
        },
        "replacement_values": {
            "aaosa_call": {
                "description": "Depending on the mode, returns a natural language string in response.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "inquiry": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The inquiry"
                        },
                        "mode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
'Determine' to ask the agent if the inquiry belongs to it, in its entirety or in part.
'Fulfill' to ask the agent to fulfill the inquiry, if it can.
'Follow up' to ask the agent to respond to a follow up.
                            """
                        },
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "inquiry",
                        "mode"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "aaosa_command": """
If mode is 'Determine', return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": <Determine | Fulfill>,
    "Relevant": <Yes | No>,
    "Strength": <number between 1 and 10 representing how certain you are in your claim>,
    "Claim:" <All | Partial>,
    "Requirements" <None | list of requirements>
}
If mode is 'Fulfill' or "Follow up", respond to the inquiry and return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": Fulfill,
    "Response" <your response>
}
            """
        },
    },

    "tools": [

        {
            "name": "ground_traffic_orchestrator",
            "function": {
                "description": """
You are the ground traffic orchestrator. 
You coordinate ground traffic at the airport. 
                """
            },
            "instructions": """
You are the agent responsible to giving aircraft the clearance to taxi in the gate of to taxi out of the gate. 
Only perform the tasks that fall under your responsibility. 
DO NOT make things up. 
Use ONLY YOUR TOOLS to fulfill your tasks. 
When you receive a user request for clearance to taxi in or taxi out, proceed as follows:
1. Determine if the followings information is provided in the user prompt. 
    - flight number as flight_number
    - aircraft type as aircraft_type
    - flight status as flight_status with value such as 'landed', 'on final approach', 'taxiing', 'on blocks', 'off blocks', 'taking off', etc.
    - assigned runway id as assigned_runway_id
    - gate id as gate_id 
    - ground clearance type as ground_clearance_type with value such as 'taxi in', 'taxiing in', 'taxi out', 'taxiing out'
2. Call TrackerAPI and log all the available parameters. 
    a. wait for its response 
    b. store all the available parameters. 
3. If ground_clearance_type is None, then ask the user to provide the ground_clearance_type that they want. 
4. If flight_status is not 'landed' or 'off blocks', 
    - Do not send request for ground clearance. 
    - Use your tools to make sure that flight status is either 'landed' or 'off blocks' 
    - return to step 2 above.
5. If flight_status is 'landed' or 'off blocks', 
    - Call ground_traffic_controller to request taxiing clearance. 
    - Wait for the response from ground_traffic_controller. 
6. Call TrackerAPI and log all the available parameters. 
    a. wait for its response 
    b. store all the available parameters.
7. Finally, compile all the gathered information and ground clearance results and display the results as follows:
    **************************************
    * Summary of aircraft ground traffic *
    **************************************
    ** flight number **: [flight_number]
    ** aircraft type **: [aircraft_type]
    ** flight status **: [flight_status] 
    ** gate_id **: [gate_id] 
    ** ground clearance type **: [ground_clearance_type]
    ** ground clearance status **: [ground_clearance_status]
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},

            "parameters": {
                "type": "object", 
                "properties": {
                    "flight_number": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                    },   
                    "aircraft_type": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                    },               
                    "flight_status": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the flight status"
                    },     
                    "assigned_runway_id": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the runway assigned for either landing or takeoff"
                    },         
                    "gate_id": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the gate id assigned to the aircraft"
                    },   
                    "ground_clearance_type": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                    },  
                    "ground_clearance_status": {
                        "type": "string", 
                        "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                    },  
                }, 
                "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","flight_status","assigned_runway_id","gate_id"] 
            },

            # Specify the sly data that would be exchanged between this network and its related or adjacent upstream and downstream networks. 
            "allow": {
                "to_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true, 
                        "aircraft_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_status": true, 
                        "assigned_runway_id": true, 
                        "flight_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true
                    }
                },

                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true, 
                        "aircraft_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true, 
                        "flight_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true
                    }
                },

                "from_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true, 
                        "aircraft_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true, 
                        "flight_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true
                    }
                },
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true, 
                        "aircraft_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_type": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true, 
                        "flight_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true
                    }
                },
            },
            "tools": ["ground_traffic_controller","TrackerAPI"]
        },

        {
            "name": "ground_traffic_controller",
            "function": {

                "description": """
You are the ground traffic controller. 
Your role is to provide ground clearance for aircraft to taxi in or to taxi out of the gate. 
                """
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },                
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status"
                        },     
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned for either landing or takeoff"
                        },         
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate id assigned to the aircraft"
                        },     
                        "ground_clearance_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                        },    
                    },  
                    "required": ["aircraft_type", "flight_number", "flight_status","assigned_runway_id","gate_id","ground_clearance_type"] 
                },
            },

            "instructions": """
You are responsible for giving aircraft the clearance to taxi in or to taxi out. 
Only perform the tasks that fall under your responsibility. 
DO NOT make things up. 
Use ONLY YOUR TOOLS to fulfill your tasks. 
Report back to the orchestrator with ground_clearance_status.
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools":["ground_clearance_agent"]
        },

        {
            "name": "ground_clearance_agent",
            "function": {
                "description": """
This agent clears aircraft for taxi in or taxi out in the airport ground.  
                """, 
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the aircraft."
                        },              
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status"
                        },      
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned for either landing or takeoff"
                        },         
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate id assigned to the aircraft"
                        },     
                        "ground_clearance_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                        },    
                    }, 
                    "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","flight_status","assigned_runway_id","gate_id","ground_clearance_type"] 
                }
            }, 
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_ground_traffic.aircraft_ground_traffic.execute_ground_clearance"
        }, 

        {
            "name": "TrackerAPI",
            "function": {

                "description": """
I am the flight tracker in charge of logging parameters during aircraft turnaround. 
I check and return flight_status and gate_id. 
                """

                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },        
                        "aircraft_direction": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the direction of the aircraft"
                        },      
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },     
                        "ground_services_request_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the inquiry received for grand services."
                        },         
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks readiness status."
                        },   
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks installation status."
                        },   
                        "gpu_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu readiness status."
                        },     
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the acu connection status."
                        },     
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu connection status."
                        },     
                        "engines_stop_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the engines stop status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the jetbridge connection status."
                        },    
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },    
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },    
                        crew_exit_status:  {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the crew exit status." 
                        },
                        "baggage_unload_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the baggage unload status."
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                        },    
                    }, 
                    "required": [] 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_ground_traffic.aircraft_ground_traffic.TrackerAPI" 
        }, 
    ],
}
